Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------PREV------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.07,0:00:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星外实习作业中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,苏茜玛斯喀维校学生一名
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.11,0:00:25.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然失去联络
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能滞留在C42废弃设施中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.63,0:00:31.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备完成后第一时间前往救援
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.63,0:00:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布斯那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.83,0:00:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己瞎走才遇难的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.27,0:00:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是自作自受吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.15,0:00:39.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:41.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氧气应该已经用完
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情况紧急
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:47.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全校一霸就此完蛋了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.98,0:00:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说这种话！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:53.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆的实习艇真的不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他真打算去救他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.83,0:00:58.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么想的 亚瑟姆？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.58,0:01:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能会被连累死的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.31,0:01:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 有人进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.33,0:01:13.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,急救措施 快！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.32,0:01:20.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 同学 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.12,0:01:25.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.58,0:01:27.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了 等在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.56,0:01:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.92,0:01:34.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昏迷中 但还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.79,0:01:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 紧急送医
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.89,0:01:38.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.94,0:01:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.66,0:01:45.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在搞什么 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.72,0:01:46.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏威
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.90,0:01:49.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太胡来了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.96,0:01:52.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么不等救援队
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.82,0:01:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那样说不定…会来不及
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.49,0:01:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时阿布斯的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,氧气罐残量…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.91,0:02:03.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,几乎是零了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.36,0:02:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人可是阿布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记他怎么对我们了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.08,0:02:11.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是两码事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.47,0:02:14.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看着有一线生机的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.31,0:02:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能见死不救… 而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:38.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.47,0:02:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是移民计划失败的受害者们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.55,0:02:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被遗弃在火星圈的人们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,建立起的新兴国家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.78,0:02:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被迫在严酷环境下生活的他们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.09,0:02:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为夺回那座名为「地球」的乐园
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.79,0:03:02.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,策划起了规模宏大的计划
