Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.40,0:05:04.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,700)}（欢庆毕业）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.61,0:05:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 装饰得好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.29,0:05:11.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是谁干的？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是一二年级生准备的惊喜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 所以才让我们典礼结束来活动室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:20.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉来早了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.29,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.58,0:05:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片打算留在这里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照片？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看这张 好怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半年前的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…可以留下它吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.49,0:05:44.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是发你数码照了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.72,0:05:47.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要的是贴在这里的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽是继续读书吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.36,0:06:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯… 本来是这么打算的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.03,0:06:02.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本来？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又…想重新考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.07,0:06:08.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暂时呆在家里
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:09.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.39,0:06:11.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆要入伍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.17,0:06:12.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么时候开始？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,假期结束以后…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.84,0:06:16.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个月以后吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.50,0:06:17.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和学校一样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.37,0:06:20.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…要加入军队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.67,0:06:22.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 没告诉过你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.47,0:06:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.59,0:06:28.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,外面那样子 比上军校好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:29.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲也这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又是父亲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:33.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你总是这么听话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.72,0:06:35.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.13,0:06:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我自己也有考虑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.54,0:06:40.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果能帮更多的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.01,0:06:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.86,0:06:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了当兵 还有很多帮助人的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:01.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗可不是慈善事业
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.42,0:07:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在是战争年代
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,参战是保护别人的最佳途径
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:14.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆要自立了 了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.54,0:07:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎终于找到了 自己力所能及的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.10,0:07:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己力所能及的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.04,0:07:26.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太装模作样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.82,0:07:28.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这里在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.58,0:07:31.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.79,0:07:33.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕业典礼要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.08,0:08:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,诸位亲爱的毕业生们
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天 我想请两位同学代表大家上台发言
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.40,0:08:12.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.37,0:08:13.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆·明日野
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:15.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请上台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.50,0:08:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校长又心血来潮了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.93,0:08:22.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.21,0:08:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上吧～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阿布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.26,0:08:46.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让开让开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.14,0:09:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 阿布斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.67,0:09:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.79,0:09:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个… 这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.35,0:09:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想 自己一辈子都不会忘记这里的岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以想对朋友 想对大家说声谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.98,0:09:58.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂喂 当我们第一天认识吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:10:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两个机动战士痴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:05.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.35,0:10:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我们平时有多迁就你们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夏威！你这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因为你们 每天才这么开心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.28,0:10:25.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:29.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,宪兵？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.85,0:10:58.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特·葛雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.62,0:11:00.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们以泄漏机密罪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即间谍罪 拘捕你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:06.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有拒绝的权力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.04,0:11:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.71,0:11:19.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没听见吗 间谍嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.73,0:11:23.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不仅如此 可能这家伙自己就是「维甘」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.52,0:11:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特不是的 他是我朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.27,0:11:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同学 老实一点会对你有好处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.09,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年前 你刚转学来到这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:44.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘就开始袭击托尔迪亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.73,0:11:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且从那以后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.28,0:11:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时常出现可疑的电波通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.81,0:11:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每次攻击前后 通讯频率增加
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.64,0:11:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要辩解就先去基地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.97,0:11:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:00.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.65,0:12:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:04.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,时间吻合 只因为这种理由
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就怀疑杰哈特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.98,0:12:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,审查任何一个有嫌疑的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.51,0:12:12.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.77,0:12:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可能是维甘…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们… 在一起好久了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.97,0:12:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.30,0:12:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别来妨碍调查
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.41,0:12:25.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想尝尝蹲牢房的滋味吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想说杰哈特骗我们？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.23,0:12:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小瞧人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.93,0:12:44.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.51,0:12:56.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:13:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.79,0:13:03.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道他才是维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.05,0:13:08.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放他跑 追！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.94,0:13:23.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.86,0:13:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧 受伤没？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.78,0:13:32.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕… 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.86,0:13:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 你从不会怀疑人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.87,0:13:43.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了 杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.12,0:13:46.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.20,0:13:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们不是朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.97,0:13:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:52.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.68,0:13:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.29,0:13:58.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好难为情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.52,0:13:59.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去卫生室吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.23,0:14:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意 保持队列
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.50,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地毯式排查
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:22.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.81,0:14:26.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切 逃进这么棘手的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.56,0:14:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,各小队 准备完毕
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.64,0:14:31.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 一只蚂蚁也别放跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.62,0:14:32.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:05.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.79,0:15:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,达斯 多亏你引起骚乱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到撤的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经吩咐多拉多队待命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:25.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们开始执行占领托尔迪亚的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:27.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白 我来指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.01,0:15:28.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.22,0:15:42.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回忆…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.99,0:15:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许停留得太久了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:50.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰达斯R 出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前确认4台维甘机动战士
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.90,0:16:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2台来自卫星外
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:17.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2台似乎潜伏在卫星内的丘陵地带
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上任不久就有一展身手的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘考虑得真是周到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.42,0:16:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,本队前往迎击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.90,0:16:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们几个 外星佬面前我看谁敢装孙子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.12,0:16:30.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.61,0:16:45.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,攻击？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.67,0:16:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是 刚才逃走的人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.24,0:16:53.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凡格斯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.29,0:16:54.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘进攻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.94,0:16:57.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卫星守军难堪重任
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.51,0:16:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆 你也出击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.42,0:17:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是高达…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.92,0:17:04.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经装车往你那里运了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到学校门前的大路上等
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.77,0:17:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.43,0:17:09.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的维甘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.56,0:17:44.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里 或许有过我渴求的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.44,0:17:46.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没有 忘记故乡的惨状
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.11,0:17:54.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种虚伪的安宁 不是战士需要的！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维甘给我 滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高达
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还留在这座卫星里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.22,0:18:32.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,驾驶的人是 亚瑟姆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.04,0:18:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙的行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.43,0:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全…全部被看穿了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:46.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:49.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反应好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.68,0:18:56.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰达斯R 果然无法跟上我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.15,0:19:00.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,面对高达 不能将就啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.33,0:19:05.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能赢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.12,0:19:40.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结束了 亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.04,0:19:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.89,0:19:47.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.53,0:19:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是那种自愿走上战场的人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.21,0:19:52.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.15,0:19:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是杰哈特吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.03,0:20:05.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:08.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你会 在那东西上面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.84,0:20:13.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的是… 维甘吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是命运
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们生在不同的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.10,0:20:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你骗了…我们吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚瑟姆
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.31,0:20:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是和你的话 也许能一直做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.21,0:20:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我作为战士肩负着责任
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有无法让步的 为之而战的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.83,0:20:46.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有吗 这样的觉悟？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.37,0:20:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是我 你能下手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:55.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种善良的家伙 不适合战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.26,0:21:05.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:28.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.59,0:21:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰哈特！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.81,0:22:24.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这种善良的家伙 不适合战斗
